org.eclipse.bpel.simpl.model
Interface ModelPackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
ModelPackage
public static interface ModelPackage.Literals

Defines literals for the meta objects that represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
